sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Admin Password Reset Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open password reset page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW-->>UI: Render reset form

    User->>UI: Submit username and new password
    UI->>LW: resetPassword()
    LW->>DB: Find user by username
    alt User not found or target is admin
        DB-->>LW: Invalid target
        LW-->>UI: Field error message
    else Valid target
        LW->>DB: Update user password
        DB-->>LW: Password updated
        LW-->>UI: Success toast + clear password fields
    end
